Title: A Worthy Challenge: Raigonn
Description:
$n, I need you to assemble a cracking group and lead them into the Gate of the Setting Sun. Activate the Challenger's Orb therein and lay waste to Raigonn.

Return to me when you've completed this challenge, and I shall reward you handsomely.
ObjectivesText: Complete the Gate of the Setting Sun Challenge Mode.
